Resolution Function (resolve-pdf-column-profile.ts)
typescript
/**
 * resolve-pdf-column-profile.ts
 *
 * Resolves the active PDF column profile for an invoice using a 4-level
 * priority chain. This function is pure (no side effects, no DB calls) —
 * callers are responsible for fetching the data and passing it in.
 *
 * Priority chain (first non-null wins):
 *   1. Per-invoice override  (invoices.pdf_column_override)
 *   2. Kostenträger Vorlage  (payers.pdf_vorlage_id → pdf_vorlagen)
 *   3. Company default       (pdf_vorlagen where is_default = true)
 *   4. System fallback       (SYSTEM_DEFAULT_* hardcoded constants)
 *
 * The returned PdfColumnProfile includes a pre-computed appendix_is_landscape
 * flag so the PDF renderer never needs to re-derive it.
 */
